{"tid":1185064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"門前風水寶地禁車輛調頭 網民玩嘢  蜂擁輪候「調頭轉運」","createTime":"2019-06-04T04:49:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T15:32:06.000Z","uid":89046,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3a4876ace559ee9a0a86b65e9883c975cc351ad0","tid":1185064,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T04:49:16.000Z","msg":"【門前風水寶地禁車輛調頭？！】<br />\n【網民玩嘢  蜂擁輪候「調頭轉運」】<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/2144634422347699/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F265944843550009%2Fposts%2F2144634422347699%2F&d=nhC78NoCA6QB0w8lKR9CgotKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=d060a69e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/265944843550009/posts/2144634422347699/</a><br />\n<br />\n近日廣東江門一棟別墅紅爆網絡，非因建築奢華，亦非因山明水秀，而是據說門前一塊地是「風水寶地」，吸引大批人騎單車、開電單車、私家車甚至連放狗都要來「調頭轉運」。深夜都有過百人圍觀樂而忘返，連警方亦出動驅散人群。<br />\n<br />\n這塊別墅前地之所以成為轉運風水寶地，事緣屋主怒氣沖沖，大力拍打車窗阻止一名女司機在他門前調頭，聲稱會破壞風水，霸道行徑引起極大迴響，於是就引發「調頭潮」。<br />\n<br />\n江門U TURN事件越演越烈，吸引周邊城市的人遠道而來。更有網民拍攝調頭攻略，教慕名來「打卡」的人：「車尾對正正門，踩三下油門，才可以完成這套動作，在這過程中，你才可以吸取這個日月精華。」<br />\n<br />\n事發地點在地圖APP上更被標註成「轉運調頭點」，事後警方封鎖該路段，禁止車輛駛入。<br />\n<br />\n#江門今期流行調頭轉運<br />\n#今晚調頭夜唔夜<br />\n#網民好想瘋狂調頭<br />\n#有線中國組"},{"pid":"e05b25cf7300acbdb478900f449bdae7c9941eba","tid":1185064,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T04:50:43.000Z","msg":"棟個牌<br />\n寫住<br />\n由好轉差 差轉更差<br />\n攪撚掂"},{"pid":"4c28181cebb3d673d9a9b94c1e864cf21710fd2d","tid":1185064,"uid":137569,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e05b25cf7300acbdb478900f449bdae7c9941eba","tid":1185064,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T04:50:43.000Z","msg":"棟個牌<br />\n寫住<br />\n由好轉差 差轉更差<br />\n攪撚掂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T04:52:56.000Z","msg":"自己心理上都會有影響"},{"pid":"22cab4df6f1187ef607b1c816d240a658d816855","tid":1185064,"uid":156130,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T04:54:57.000Z","msg":"d鄉音好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdd0a2398eb39c009d1672b19210d983c6e9b902","tid":1185064,"uid":60052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22cab4df6f1187ef607b1c816d240a658d816855","tid":1185064,"uid":156130,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T04:54:57.000Z","msg":"d鄉音好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T05:19:46.000Z","msg":"即刻諗起1212屌你個西"},{"pid":"b011094618c5a016cb9cdb7e7f6f491f36986bbd","tid":1185064,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T05:20:58.000Z","msg":"支國只有地獄<br />\n<br />\n不存在寶地"},{"pid":"12a4094df02712a65e290336b95abcd080c8bc6a","tid":1185064,"uid":9694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T06:05:06.000Z","msg":"呢下報復好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78eafba6d93563fc0428647e57b21ac01bdc558f","tid":1185064,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T15:32:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}